OL,3,COlympians and Paralympians back plan
OL,4,Cfor north of England games bid
OL,6,FMore than 40 Olympians, Paralympians
OL,7,Fand elite athletes including Sir Jason
OL,8,FKenny and Dame Sarah Storey have
OL,9,Fbacked a potential bid to bring the
OL,10,Fgames to the north of England.
OL,12,FMinisters announced last month that
OL,13,Fthey would carry out an assessment
OL,14,Fwhich could inform a bid for the
OL,15,FOlympics and Paralympics in the 2040s.
OL,17,FThe strategic assessment by UK Sport
OL,18,Fwill examine the costs, the socio-
OL,19,Feconomic benefits to the north, and
OL,20,Fthe bid's chance of success.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
