OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782220722
OL,3,COlympians and Paralympians back plan
OL,4,Cfor north of England games bid
OL,6,FOn Tuesday (23 June), northern mayors
OL,7,FOliver Coppard, Kim McGuinness, Tracy
OL,8,FBrabin, David Skaith and Luke Campbell
OL,9,Fwill hold an event at the Olympic
OL,10,FLegacy Park in Sheffield to discuss
OL,11,Fhow the north of England can develop a
OL,12,F"credible, deliverable vision" for the
OL,13,Fgames.
OL,15,FIn their statement, athletes say a
OL,16,Fnorthern-hosted Games would be "a
OL,17,Fmoment of renewal and confidence for
OL,18,Fthe entire United Kingdom".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
