PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782220722
OL,3,COlympians and Paralympians back plan
OL,4,Cfor north of England games bid
OL,6,FIt read: "As Olympians, Paralympians,
OL,7,Fathletes and competitors who have had
OL,8,Fthe honour of representing Great
OL,9,FBritain and competing on the highest
OL,10,Fstage, we write to express our strong
OL,11,Fand united support for the north of
OL,12,FEngland to host a future Olympic and
OL,13,FParalympic Games.
OL,15,F"The legacy of the London 2012 Summer
OL,16,FOlympics and Paralympics showed what
OL,17,Fis possible when the country comes
OL,18,Ftogether behind a shared ambition. Now
OL,19,Fis the moment to build on that legacy.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782220722
OL,3,COlympians and Paralympians back plan
OL,4,Cfor north of England games bid
OL,6,F"Many of us have seen first-hand that
OL,7,Fthe north of England has the ability
OL,8,Fto host a box-office Games: world-
OL,9,Fclass venues, experienced event hosts
OL,10,Fand a passion for sport like no other
OL,11,Fplace."
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782220722
OL,3,COlympians and Paralympians back plan
OL,4,Cfor north of England games bid
OL,6,FIt continues: "Few moments unite the
OL,7,Fcountry like the Olympic and
OL,8,FParalympic Games. We have felt that
OL,9,Funity ` in packed stadiums, in town
OL,10,Fsquares, in schools and living rooms
OL,11,Facross the country.
OL,13,F"A 'Great North' Games would be a
OL,14,Fnational Games. It would bring the
OL,15,Fcountry together in common purpose. It
OL,16,Fwould showcase the very best of Great
OL,17,FBritain.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782220722
OL,3,COlympians and Paralympians back plan
OL,4,Cfor north of England games bid
OL,6,F"We believe that hosting a Games in
OL,7,Fthe north of England in 2040 would be
OL,8,Fa moment of renewal and confidence for
OL,9,Fthe entire United Kingdom.
OL,11,F"We are proud to add our voices to
OL,12,Fthis vision and to support a northern
OL,13,FGames that would inspire generations
OL,14,Fto come."
OL,16,FThe findings of the initial assessment
OL,17,Fwill determine whether a more detailed
OL,18,Ftechnical feasibility study is
OL,19,Fundertaken to examine costs, benefits
OL,20,Fand viability of hosting the Games.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
